595
00:24:49.480 --> 00:24:51.272
<i>She kept asking if her
friend Linda was here.</i>

596
00:24:51.273 --> 00:24:52.899
<i>and when I told her
it was illegal for me</i>

597
00:24:52.900 --> 00:24:55.110
<i>to disclose anything about the
