611
00:25:22.930 --> 00:25:24.389
You asked about Linda.
right?

612
00:25:24.390 --> 00:25:26.391
I know that your boyfriend's
ex-wife is named Linda.

613
00:25:26.392 --> 00:25:29.102
You're crazy.

614
00:25:29.103 --> 00:25:32.147
Did he tell you to ask
