676
00:28:01.088 --> 00:28:03.506
but off-hours... I
mean. you're a little...

677
00:28:03.507 --> 00:28:05.508
Easy target. A push over.

678
00:28:05.509 --> 00:28:08.011
Hmm. Alright. The good news
